title: [Silken Mist, Lifeboat]
description: The luxury of the ship does not stop at the bow, even the lifeboat has been graciously appointed.  Supplies that would hold out for several weeks have been stored under one bench, and the contents of the many assorted jars and boxes would make even the finickiest gourmand happy.
room.location: Silken Mist on Four Winds Isle
